{"tid":2056151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【Jupas改選】浸大，教大及中大成最大贏家","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T13:09:53.000Z","uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0485e1f99ff5c6399529ec642b1b206bdd9f9243","tid":2056151,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBPX5gm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBPX5gm.png&h=81a2bc03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9sF221.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9sF221.png&h=75313229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bX9ARWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbX9ARWn.jpg&h=9b7119b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學聯招（JUPAS）改選前日（3日）截止，各大學今日（5日）公布課程的報讀情況，護理學和幼兒教育繼續成為熱門課程，香港大學和中文大學的護理學課程分別有1,900和1,737人報讀（列為首三志願，下同），是較多人報讀的熱門課程；至於中文大學和教育大學的幼兒教育課程，分別有48.4人和38.6人爭一學位，屬競爭較激烈的課程。<br />\n<br />\n今年JUPAS競爭最激烈的課程是僅有12個學額的浸會大學動畫及媒體藝術專修，有664人報讀，平均55.3人爭一學位。同一學院開辦的浸大電影電視專修競爭亦激烈，713人爭奪20個學額，平均35.7人爭一學位。中大和教大的幼兒教育課程亦是競爭激烈的課程，分別有1,016和1,889人報讀，爭奪21和49個學額，平均48.4和38.6人爭一學位。<br />\n<br />\n以將課程列為首三志願計算，今年港大護理學吸引1,990人報讀爭奪210個學位，其次是教大幼兒教育（1,889人報讀）、中大工商管理（1,824人報讀）、中大理學（1,821人報讀），以及中大護理學（1,737人報讀）。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/2PVLA7HE7ZYVC2V5S544SZH42A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F2PVLA7HE7ZYVC2V5S544SZH42A%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=57b46351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200605%2F2PVLA7HE7ZYVC2V5S544SZH42A%2F&h=ccda1e89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200605/2PVLA7HE7ZYVC2V5S544SZH42A/</a>"},{"pid":"2fc729d8c2740261d9fbaae950f792078f2a1971","tid":2056151,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:09:53.000Z","msg":"CU 既IBBA？？？？？"}]}